metadata.name: Strokes of Winds #1
metadata.description:
Since I began studying spontaneous and ambiguous painting several years ago, I have become fascinated with artists such as Johannes Vermeer, Edgar Degas, and Van Gogh. The first collection, which I call Whisper Winds of Life, is finally ready for release. In its command and resilience, wind shows a life of freedom and unrestricted living. 

~Artco
